export const text = `
<ToolTip content="tooltip" direction="top" position="40" delay={1000}>
<Button>click</Button>
</ToolTip>
<ToolTip
content="tooltip"
direction="bottom"
position="40"
delay={1000}
>
<Button>click</Button>
</ToolTip>
`;
